To plot indicator values, in the OnData event handler, call the Plot method.

private KickingByLength _kickingbylength;

// In Initialize()
var symbol = AddEquity("SPY").Symbol;
_kickingbylength = KickingByLength(symbol);

// In OnData()
if (_kickingbylength.IsReady)
{
    Plot("My Indicators", "KickingByLength Period", _kickingbylength.Period);
    Plot("My Indicators", "KickingByLength Current", _kickingbylength.Current);
